@why.bsky.team The prototype of N-Feed, which until now had remained only an idea, has finally been completed.
It is a feed that lists three posts with keywords that your post contains. Currently, it is available only for Japanese posts.
My lab member, Mr. Shigepon (@shigepon.net) , created it.

